text: Poul Jessen (17 February 1926 - 16 June 2015) was a Danish gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
